{"id": 59726, "date": "2025-09-23T04:00:14", "date_gmt": "2025-09-23T11:00:14", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59726"}, "modified": "2026-05-25T09:10:57", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-25T16:10:57", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-23-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/23/kingdom-of-days-september-23-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 23"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1949:\u00a0</strong>Bruce Frederick Joseph Springsteen is born to Adele and Douglas Springsteen at Monmouth Medical Center in Long Branch, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12853\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1949-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1949-09-23.jpg?fit=375%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"375,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1949-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1949-09-23.jpg?fit=375%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12853 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1949-09-23.jpg?resize=375%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1949-09-23.jpg?w=375&amp;ssl=1 375w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1949-09-23.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4478\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1949-0923/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1949-0923.jpeg?fit=620%2C448&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"620,448\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1949-0923\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1949-0923.jpeg?fit=620%2C448&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4478 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1949-0923.jpeg?resize=620%2C448&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1949-0923.jpeg?w=620&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1949-0923.jpeg?resize=300%2C217&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1952:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s parents throw their three-year-old son a Western-themed birthday party. Bruce&#8217;s fascination with the American west will last a lifetime.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21354\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1952-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?fit=1958%2C1392&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1958,1392\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600351213&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1952-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?fit=758%2C539&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21354 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?resize=758%2C539&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"539\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?w=1958&amp;ssl=1 1958w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?resize=300%2C213&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?resize=1024%2C728&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?resize=768%2C546&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1952-09-23.jpg?resize=1536%2C1092&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>On his 24th birthday, Bruce records two of his greatest songs: &#8220;Incident on 57th Street&#8221; and &#8220;Rosalita (Come Out Tonight).&#8221; With these songs in the can, Bruce&#8217;s second album is complete.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ioQcvijom28?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JuVKhS13eKY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his first known birthday show, turning in a great performance at the University of Michigan in Ann Arbor on the day he turns 26. In the encores, Bruce and the E Street Band play &#8220;Detroit Medley&#8221; for the very first time.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/t87UMZI1cnE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21355\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?fit=1476%2C1641&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1476,1641\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600351758&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?fit=758%2C843&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21355 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?resize=758%2C843&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"843\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?w=1476&amp;ssl=1 1476w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?resize=270%2C300&amp;ssl=1 270w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?resize=921%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 921w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?resize=768%2C854&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-23.jpg?resize=1382%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1382w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce spends his 29th birthday in Asbury Park with interviewer Mike Greenblatt and photographer Bob Sorce for <em>The Aquarian.</em></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4484\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0923/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0923.jpg?fit=258%2C640&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"258,640\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0923\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0923.jpg?fit=258%2C640&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4484 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0923.jpg?resize=258%2C640&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"258\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0923.jpg?w=258&amp;ssl=1 258w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0923.jpg?resize=121%2C300&amp;ssl=1 121w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce spends his 35th birthday on roller skates with friends and bandmates at United Skates of America in Buffalo. He&#8217;s not very good, but with a girl on each arm, he manages to stay upright&#8230; most of the time.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"59748\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/23/kingdom-of-days-september-23-2/usa_today_1984_09_26_22/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?fit=513%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"513,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"USA_Today_1984_09_26_22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?fit=205%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-59748 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?resize=513%2C2560&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"2560\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?w=513&amp;ssl=1 513w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?resize=60%2C300&amp;ssl=1 60w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?resize=205%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 205w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/USA_Today_1984_09_26_22-scaled.jpg?resize=308%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 308w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce spends his 36th birthday on stage at Denver&#8217;s Mile High Stadium. The night is unseasonably cold, with temperatures dropping into the 30s. The result is a relatively quiet crowd&#8211;they&#8217;re clapping with gloves on!</p>\n<div id=\"v-Bpja26tF-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Bpja26tF?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></scr