e=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?fit=1128%2C1651&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1128,1651\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600352443&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-23c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?fit=700%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21358 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?resize=758%2C1109&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1109\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?w=1128&amp;ssl=1 1128w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?resize=205%2C300&amp;ssl=1 205w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?resize=700%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?resize=768%2C1124&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-23c.jpg?resize=1049%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1049w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4495\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-0923/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0923.jpg?fit=252%2C461&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"252,461\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-0923\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0923.jpg?fit=252%2C461&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4495 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0923.jpg?resize=252%2C461&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"252\" height=\"461\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0923.jpg?w=252&amp;ssl=1 252w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0923.jpg?resize=164%2C300&amp;ssl=1 164w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1986:\u00a0</strong>A group of teenage fans gather in Bruce&#8217;s driveway late at night to wish him a happy 37th birthday. Bruce is not amused.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21359\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1986-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?fit=1218%2C1639&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1218,1639\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600352651&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1986-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?fit=758%2C1020&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21359 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?resize=758%2C1020&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1020\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?w=1218&amp;ssl=1 1218w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?resize=223%2C300&amp;ssl=1 223w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?resize=761%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 761w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?resize=768%2C1033&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1986-09-23.jpg?resize=1141%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1141w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>A special Human Rights Now! show in Oakland on the occasion of Bruce&#8217;s 39th birthday: Roy Orbison surprises Bruce backstage and leads the crowd in singing &#8220;Happy Birthday,&#8221; as does Joan Baez, who also performs &#8220;Blowin&#8217; in the Wind&#8221; with Bruce. During Bruce&#8217;s set, he tour premieres &#8220;Tunnel of Love&#8221; and plays his very first &#8220;I Ain&#8217;t Got No Home.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-nGfxpXnuBQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pZ-8l_MjUlU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDpZ-8l_MjUlU\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-ObIM11p3-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ObIM11p3?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29513\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1988-09-23a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1988-09-23a.jpg?fit=798%2C1845&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"798,1845\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600353103&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1988-09-2