-image-21361 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?resize=758%2C828&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"828\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?w=1507&amp;ssl=1 1507w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?resize=274%2C300&amp;ssl=1 274w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?resize=937%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 937w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?resize=768%2C839&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1988-09-23b.jpg?resize=1405%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1405w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce celebrates his 40th birthday with the E Street Band (including Steve Van Zandt, who sings lead on &#8220;Stand By Me&#8221; so Bruce can have a dance with his mom) at McLoone&#8217;s Rum Runner in Sea Bright. This is the last E Street Band performance before Bruce disbands them.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21362\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?fit=659%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"659,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600353406&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?fit=410%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21362 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?resize=659%2C1647&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"659\" height=\"1647\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?w=659&amp;ssl=1 659w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?resize=120%2C300&amp;ssl=1 120w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?resize=410%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 410w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23.jpg?resize=615%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 615w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21363\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-09-23b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?fit=1381%2C1648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1381,1648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600353488&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-09-23b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?fit=758%2C905&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21363 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?resize=758%2C905&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"905\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?w=1381&amp;ssl=1 1381w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?resize=251%2C300&amp;ssl=1 251w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?resize=858%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 858w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?resize=768%2C916&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1989-09-23b.jpg?resize=1287%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1287w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1997:\u00a0</strong>Bruce celebrates his 48th birthday with friends and family at his house in Colts Neck. The entertainment for the evening is a local band called The Gotham Playboys that Soozie Tyrell clued Bruce into, and Bruce is so taken with them that he will shortly hire several of the group&#8217;s members to play on the first of what would become known as The Seeger Sessions.</p>\n<p><strong>2014:\u00a0</strong>At a special event at Monmouth University, Thom Zimny screens never-before-seen (and never-again-seen) archival clips from Bruce&#8217;s vault.</p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>On the occasion of Bruce&#8217;s 67th birthday, he releases his\u00a0<em>Chapter and Verse</em> retrospective companion CD to his autobiography, <em>Born to Run.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_knar_COIQJmNAfQMAjQ5PLi7SwhH710Xc\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21364\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2016-09-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?fit=1675%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1675,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600354295&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2016-09-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?fit=758%2C745&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21364 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=758%2C745&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"745\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?w=1675&amp;ssl=1 1675w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=300%2C295&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=1024%2C1007&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=768%2C755&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=1536%2C1510&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-09-23.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong>Bruce announces a new concert film,\u00a0<em>The 1979 Legendary No Nukes Concerts.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HUO41TDicD0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>It&#8217;s Bruce&#8217;s birthday! You&#8217;d think that&#8217;d be enough highlight for one date, but there&#8217;s more: the release of Chapter and Verse, the last E Street Band performance before the break-up, the origin of the Seeger Sessions Band, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 12860, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [1605, 558, 1568, 567, 439, 1606, 1354, 977, 60, 1584, 528, 1600, 383, 109], "class_list": ["post-59726", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-th